Socket server for management game.

==== What is it? ====
This is implementation of university task. For full game rules
(not implemented in this) see [1]. For task and reduced rules see [2].

==== Notes ====
Used buffer.[ch] from https://github.com/Totktonada/shell .

==== Books ====
[1] Chales Wetherell "Etudes for programmers"
    (the book has english and russian releases).
[2] http://www.stolyarov.info/books/gameserv
    (only in russian).
